---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Events" description="Upcoming events, shows and meetings at the Torbay Garden Club.">

  <div style="height: 64px;"></div>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Living Calendar</span>
      <h1 class="heading-display">Events <em>&amp; Shows</em></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="events-full">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="events-intro">
        <p>From our beloved Spring Show to monthly meetings and garden trips, there's always something growing in our calendar.</p>
        <p>We meet on the first Wednesday of each month (except January, February and July) at the Torbay Community Hall, 35 Watea Road, Torbay. Meetings begin at 1:00pm.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Filter bar -->
      <div class="event-filter">
        <button class="event-filter-btn active" data-filter="upcoming">Upcoming</button>
        <button class="event-filter-btn" data-filter="past">Past Events</button>
      </div>

      <!-- UPCOMING EVENTS -->
      <div class="event-section" id="upcoming">
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot dot-filled"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <div class="event-card-inner">
                <div class="event-card-image">
                  <img src="/ss26-event.jpg" alt="Spring Show 2026" />
                </div>
                <div class="event-card-body">
                  <div class="event-tags">
                    <span class="event-tag tag-public">Public Event</span>
                    <span class="event-tag tag-next">Next Up</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3>Spring Show 2026</h3>
                  <p>The Torbay Garden Club has held a Spring Show for many years. It's a great opportunity to show off plants or flowers from your garden and enjoy the gardening wonders on show. Bring your friends and family along!</p>
                  <div class="event-meta">
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg> Wednesday 2nd September 2026</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg> 12:00pm — 2:00pm</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 21s-8-7.5-8-12a8 8 0 1 1 16 0c0 4.5-8 12-8 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg> Torbay Community Hall, 35 Watea Rd, Torbay</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="event-entry">Entry: Open to the public, $2 door entry</p>
                  <div class="event-divider"></div>
                  <ul class="event-details">
                    <li>Raffle and trading table with great bargains for your garden</li>
                    <li>Children's sections for preschool kids</li>
                    <li>Entries: Jar of flowers (6-12 stems) and Fruit/Vegetable creature</li>
                    <li>Winners receive cash prizes as per the schedule</li>
                    <li>Entries must be staged from 9:30am to 10:40am on the day</li>
                    <li>No fees for entering exhibits</li>
                  </ul>
                  <div class="event-footer">
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/4519009988345515" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="facebook-link">
                      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
                      View on Facebook
                    </a>
                    <div class="event-footer-buttons">
                      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeP4UkKyB06vpTzcdxEm27l0nlLuNKIQb9fxeHZUYhmih0ZbQ/viewform?usp=publish-editor" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="schedule-btn">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
                        Register Entries
                      </a>
                      <a href="/SpringShow2026-Schedule.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="schedule-btn">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
                        Download Schedule
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot dot-empty"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <div class="event-card-inner">
                <div class="event-card-image">
                  <img src="/monthlymeeting.jpg" alt="Monthly Meeting" />
                </div>
                <div class="event-card-body">
                  <div class="event-tags">
                    <span class="event-tag tag-monthly">Monthly</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3>Monthly Meetings</h3>
                  <p>Regular club meetings with guest speakers, club show, raffle, trading table, and morning tea. Visitors always welcome — free entry.</p>
                  <div class="event-meta">
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg> First Wednesday of each month (excl. Jan, Feb, Jul)</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg> 1:00pm</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 21s-8-7.5-8-12a8 8 0 1 1 16 0c0 4.5-8 12-8 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg> Torbay Community Hall, 35 Watea Rd, Torbay</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PAST EVENTS -->
      <div class="event-section hidden" id="past">
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-line"></div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot dot-filled"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <div class="event-card-inner">
                <div class="event-card-image">
                  <img src="/ss25-event.jpg" alt="Spring Show 2025" />
                </div>
                <div class="event-card-body">
                  <div class="event-tags">
                    <span class="event-tag tag-public">Public Event</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3>Spring Show 2025</h3>
                  <p>The Torbay Garden Club has held a Spring Show for many years. It's a great opportunity to show off plants or flowers from your garden and enjoy the gardening wonders on show. Bring your friends and family along!</p>
                  <div class="event-meta">
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg> Saturday 6th September 2025</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg> 12:30pm — 3:00pm</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 21s-8-7.5-8-12a8 8 0 1 1 16 0c0 4.5-8 12-8 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg> Torbay Community Hall, 35 Watea Rd, Torbay</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="event-entry">Entry: Open to the public, $2 door entry</p>
                  <div class="event-divider"></div>
                  <ul class="event-details">
                    <li>Raffle and trading table with great bargains for your garden</li>
                    <li>Children's sections for preschoolers and primary school kids</li>
                    <li>Entries: Jar of flowers (6-12 stems) and Fruit/Vegetable creature</li>
                    <li>Winners receive cash prizes as per the schedule</li>
                    <li>Entries must be staged from 9:30am to 10:45am on the day</li>
                    <li>No fees for entering exhibits</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot dot-empty"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <div class="event-card-inner">
                <div class="event-card-image">
                  <img src="/roseshow25.png" alt="Rose Show 2025" />
                </div>
                <div class="event-card-body">
                  <div class="event-tags">
                    <span class="event-tag tag-members">Members</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3>Rose Show 2025</h3>
                  <p>The November Rose Show is a chance for club members to showcase their favourite and best roses from their gardens.</p>
                  <div class="event-meta">
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg> Wednesday 5th November 2025</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg> 1:00pm — 2:00pm</span>
                    <span><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 21s-8-7.5-8-12a8 8 0 1 1 16 0c0 4.5-8 12-8 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg> Torbay Community Hall, 35 Watea Rd, Torbay</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="event-entry">Entry: Club Members, Friends &amp; Family only</p>
                  <div class="event-divider"></div>
                  <p style="font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Rose exhibits are restricted to club members only. Please note that the standard monthly show will also take place, but there is no "Class 1: Flower of the Month".</p>
                  <ul class="event-details">
                    <li>Winners of the sections will receive cash prizes as per the schedule</li>
                    <li>Entries must be staged from 11:30am to 12:25pm on the day</li>
                    <li>There are no fees for entering exhibits in the Show</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:1rem;">For questions or more information email <a href="mailto:torbaygardenclub@gmail.com" style="color:var(--crimson);">torbaygardenclub@gmail.com</a></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const filterBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.event-filter-btn');
  const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.event-section');

  filterBtns.forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      filterBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
const filter = (btn as HTMLElement).dataset.filter;
      sections.forEach(section => {
        if (section.id === filter) {
          section.classList.remove('hidden');
        } else {
          section.classList.add('hidden');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
.page-hero { padding: 4rem 0 0.5rem; }
.events-full { padding: 1.5rem 2rem 5rem; }
.events-intro { max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.events-intro p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

/* Filter bar */
.event-filter {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
}
.event-filter-btn {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  margin-bottom: -2px;
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.event-filter-btn:hover { color: var(--charcoal); }
.event-filter-btn.active { color: var(--crimson); border-bottom-color: var(--crimson); }

.hidden { display: none; }

/* Timeline */
.timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 2.5rem; }
.timeline-line { position: absolute; left: 0.5rem; top: 0.5rem; bottom: 0.5rem; width: 1px; background: var(--border); }
.timeline-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.timeline-dot { position: absolute; left: -2rem; top: 1.5rem; width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid var(--crimson); }
.dot-filled { background: var(--crimson); }
.dot-empty { background: var(--cream); }
.timeline-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
.event-card-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 0; }
.event-card-image { flex-shrink: 0; }
.event-card-image img { width: 200px; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
.event-card-body { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
.event-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.event-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 2px; }
.tag-public { background: #fce8ed; color: var(--crimson); }
.tag-members { background: var(--cream-dark); color: var(--text-muted); }
.tag-monthly { background: var(--cream-dark); color: var(--text-muted); }
.tag-next { background: var(--crimson); color: var(--white); }
.timeline-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
.timeline-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.event-meta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.2rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.event-meta span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
.event-entry { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--crimson); margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
.event-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 1rem 0; }
.event-details { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.event-details li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); padding-left: 1.2rem; position: relative; }
.event-details li::before { content: '•'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--charcoal); }
.events-year-heading { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .event-card-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .event-card-image img { width: 100%; height: 200px; }
}
.facebook-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  color: #1877f2;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.facebook-link:hover { opacity: 0.75; }
.schedule-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--crimson);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--crimson);
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}
.schedule-btn:hover {
  background: var(--crimson);
  color: var(--white);
}
.event-footer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.event-footer .facebook-link {
  margin-right: auto;
}
.event-footer-buttons {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  align-items: flex-end;
}
</style>